    "Your data is safe with us": "Data yako iko salama kwetu",
    "SmartBiz transformed how I track my inventory. I used to lose stock weekly, now I know exactly what I have and what I need to order.": "SmartBiz ilibadilisha jinsi ninavyofuatilia hesabu zangu. Nilikuwa nikipoteza hisa kila wiki, sasa najua hasa kile nilicho na kile ninachohitaji kuagiza.",
    "The credit sales feature is a lifesaver. I can now track who owes me and when payments are due. My cash flow has improved dramatically.": "Kipengele cha mauzo ya mkopo ni wokovu. Sasa ninaweza kufuatilia nani ananidai na malipo yanapotakiwa. Mtiririko wangu wa fedha umeimarika kwa kiasi kikubwa.",
    "I manage three employees and the reporting helps me see who is performing. The AI assistant answers my questions instantly. Worth every shilling!": "Ninasimamia wafanyakazi watatu na ripoti hunisaidia kuona anayefanya vizuri. Kisaidizi cha AI kinajibu maswali yangu papo hapo. Inastahili kila shilingi!",
    "Setting up was so easy. I uploaded my products in minutes and started selling the same day. The dashboard gives me everything I need at a glance.": "Kusanidi ilikuwa rahisi sana. Nilibeba bidhaa zangu kwa dakika na kuanza kuuza siku hiyo hiyo. Dashibodi inanipa kila kitu ninachohitaji kwa mtazamo.",
    "As a wholesaler, I deal with bulk stock and dozens of products daily. SmartBiz makes inventory management smooth and my profit tracking is now accurate.": "Kama mfanyabiashara wa jumla, ninashughulika na hisa nyingi na makumi ya bidhaa kila siku. SmartBiz inafanya usimamizi wa hesabu kuwa laini na ufuatiliaji wangu wa faida sasa ni sahihi.",
    "I run a boutique and a small salon. Having both inventory and expense tracking in one system saves me hours every week. Highly recommend!": "Ninaendesha boutique na saluni ndogo. Kuwa na ufuatiliaji wa hesabu na gharama katika mfumo mmoja kunaniokoa saa nyingi kila wiki. Ninapendekeza sana!",
    "SmartBiz transformed how I track my inventory. I used to lose stock weekly, now I know exactly what I have and what I need to order. The real-time stock updates alone have saved me from overselling multiple times.": "SmartBiz ilibadilisha jinsi ninavyofuatilia hesabu zangu. Nilikuwa nikipoteza hisa kila wiki, sasa najua hasa kile nilicho na kile ninachohitaji kuagiza. Sasisho za hisa kwa wakati halisi pekee zimeniokoa kutokana na kuuza zaidi mara nyingi.",
    "The credit sales feature is a lifesaver. I can now track who owes me and when payments are due. My cash flow has improved dramatically since I started using SmartBiz. The repayment reminders are a game changer.": "Kipengele cha mauzo ya mkopo ni wokovu. Sasa ninaweza kufuatilia nani ananidai na malipo yanapotakiwa. Mtiririko wangu wa fedha umeimarika kwa kiasi kikubwa tangu nilipoanza kutumia SmartBiz. Vikumbusho vya ulipaji vimebadilisha mchezo.",
    "I manage three employees and the reporting helps me see who is performing. The AI assistant answers my questions instantly. Worth every shilling! The financial position report gives me a clear picture of my business health.": "Ninasimamia wafanyakazi watatu na ripoti hunisaidia kuona anayefanya vizuri. Kisaidizi cha AI kinajibu maswali yangu papo hapo. Inastahili kila shilingi! Ripoti ya hali ya kifedha inanipa picha wazi ya afya ya biashara yangu.",
    "Setting up was so easy. I uploaded my products in minutes and started selling the same day. The dashboard gives me everything I need at a glance — daily sales, expenses, and profit all in one place.": "Kusanidi ilikuwa rahisi sana. Nilibeba bidhaa zangu kwa dakika na kuanza kuuza siku hiyo hiyo. Dashibodi inanipa kila kitu ninachohitaji kwa mtazamo \\u2014 mauzo ya kila siku, gharama, na faida vyote mahali pamoja.",
    "As a wholesaler, I deal with bulk stock and dozens of products daily. SmartBiz makes inventory management smooth and my profit tracking is now accurate. The bulk upload feature saves me hours every week.": "Kama mfanyabiashara wa jumla, ninashughulika na hisa nyingi na makumi ya bidhaa kila siku. SmartBiz inafanya usimamizi wa hesabu kuwa laini na ufuatiliaji wangu wa faida sasa ni sahihi. Kipengele cha upakiaji kwa wingi kinaniokoa saa nyingi kila wiki.",
    "I run a boutique and a small salon. Having both inventory and expense tracking in one system saves me hours every week. Highly recommend! The employee management feature helps me track my team's performance too.": "Ninaendesha boutique na saluni ndogo. Kuwa na ufuatiliaji wa hesabu na gharama katika mfumo mmoja kunaniokoa saa nyingi kila wiki. Ninapendekeza sana! Kipengele cha usimamizi wa wafanyakazi kinanisaidia kufuatilia utendaji wa timu yangu pia.",
